                      "value": ""
                    },
                    "title": {
                      "value": ""
                    },
                    "text": {
                      "value": "<p style=\"font-weight:700;\">The Rolex Awards for Enterprise identify and invest in exceptional people seeking solutions to humankind’s most pressing challenges. These visionary individuals are united by a commitment to improve life and protect our planet. They have in common the ability to embrace projects that require creativity and determination in the face of considerable odds.<p>\n<p>Rolex is seeking innovative projects in the five following areas: science and health; the environment; applied technology; exploration; cultural heritage. The five Laureates will receive substantial funding and worldwide publicity to assist with their projects. They will also be granted access to the Rolex community of Laureates for advice and guidance.</p>"
                    },
                    "linkLabel": {
                      "value": ""
                    },
